    <h1>Microjam</h1>
    <div class="project_card">
        <img src="/images/microjam.png" alt="Gameboy Advance game Microjam">
        <p>Worked on a collaborative project with my class on a Gameboy Advance game. I worked with a partner to design and develop a mini game for this game called Planetoids. 
            In this game, the goal is to destroy some asteroids to beat the game. The number of asteroids is dependent on the difficulty level of the overall game.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/grc-cohort-23/microjam" target="_blank"><p>GitHub Repository</p></a>
    </div>
    <h1>Game Deal Finder Web App</h1>
    <div class="project_card">
        <img src="/images/deal_finder.png" alt="Home page of the Game Deal Finder web app">
        <p>Worked on a team of three to design and develop a Node web app. The app we decided to develop is a user form for game deals. Any user can submit a game deal they find
             on and any user will be able to see that deal on the home page of the app. </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/akurfurst/CodeRelic-GameDealFinder"><p>GitHub Repository</p></a>
